channel.title: Auto Cache Downloader Help
channel.description: Hello, my name is Jon and i have been having a little issue with a new server I made. After 5 nights of total BS we got the server running. We found our source that we plan to stick with forever. I am using rswebclients and its total crap. I really want a auto cache downloader. I want it because i would like to make a custom webclient on my website to make the server better and more official. Another problem, i just ordered a vps yesterday and got the verification for it today and it was 22.48. I am a little broke so please if you help dont ask for money. It's annoyying :( Anyways thanks for reading my skype username is: gayboy3331. No i am not gay lol please don't ask. If you want to reply you can add me on skype or post on here. Whatever works for you :)
